-- Harper Leans Toward Approving to BHP Billiton's Potash Bid, FT Reports
-- B y   V i c t o r i a   R i c h a r d s
-- 2010-10-28T23:44:10Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-28/canada-may-give-approval-to-bhp-on-potash-bid-ft-says.html
Canada’s Conservative government is
leaning towards granting approval for BHP Billiton Ltd.’s
takeover offer for Potash Corp. of Saskatchewan Inc., the
Financial Times said, citing several unidentified people with
close connections to the government. Canada’s industry
department and BHP are in the final stages of negotiating a
package intended to show the merits of a deal to the country,
the FT reported.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Victoria Richards at 
 vrichards@bloomberg.net  